{"tid":1719181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國有個中國委員會架，人地撐香港，你唔係唔知呀吓？","createTime":"2019-11-14T04:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T06:34:09.000Z","uid":264873,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9613f2ee52b977cf578b72e6773e6b1463bbb328","tid":1719181,"uid":264873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:44:24.000Z","msg":"話說今朝見到下面呢個消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，話兩黨重量級議員成功逼宮，參院即將審議法案，嘩，希望堅係好快審議通過啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zE15ZQp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzE15ZQp.jpg&h=7cbab0af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到美國嘅支持，呢篇推文成串thread都好值得<span style=\"color: orange;\">like + retweet + comment</span>！<br />\n<br />\n呢篇咩黎？係美國議會嘅<span style=\"color: blue;\">China Commission (CECC)</span>發表嘅，咩係CECC？下面貼埋資料俾你，自己睇啦!<br />\n<br />\n成串thread一路講到<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後講出咗香港嘅自主性如果仆咗街，對世界嘅政治、金融、社會都有影響!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/CECCgov/status/1194747126523269121?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCECCgov%2Fstatus%2F1194747126523269121%3Fs%3D09&d=7CNMK8%2FfTiCK2iXV1c%2BwrAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=001c6974\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCECCgov%2Fstatus%2F1194747126523269121%3Fs%3D09&h=e68f6785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/CECCgov/status/1194747126523269121?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n[img]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5cAOc4m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5cAOc4m.jpg&h=2567a5e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[img]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdEGx4x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsdEGx4x.jpg&h=b3bf8095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[img]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WJsXQSJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWJsXQSJ.jpg&h=a457038d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[img]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gG6arrb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgG6arrb.jpg&h=a839c5ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCECC:<br />\n<br />\n[img]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CTbBmZJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCTbBmZJ.jpg&h=9020f3a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCECC 係佢兩個Chair架，係咪好熟口面？<br />\n右邊果位Marco Rubio，咪就係喺參議院推香港人權與民主法嘅大佬囉！大家仲唔快啲去回應下就唔係人啦屌！<br />\n<br />\n[img]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ZuGx7x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ZuGx7x.jpg&h=bf327d4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"277de353f10a2f22188e9bb0ad0d9393eb32f09a","tid":1719181,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58389ffbe6d4223f963b7366a1179df8186240d","tid":1719181,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:47:33.000Z","msg":"pushhhh"},{"pid":"e5cd722e5f19a99ea73043e245bfa666ecbb4679","tid":1719181,"uid":82955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:48:02.000Z","msg":"[文宣升級&mdash;要追上前線行動呀！]<br />\n解鎖新職業 &mdash; 郵差叔叔，速遞員！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1717313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1717313</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，手足，借個位，認同請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發生好多事，好多怨案，令我地好嬲好嬲。但文宣一定要做足做好，我地係為正義而戰，我地從來都唔係暴徒！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arAivP6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarAivP6.png&h=a9a1a627&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSLZfgM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSLZfgM.jpg&h=20bdb60e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70bc78b835351e730e1be86c9fff5e56b8359ca5","tid":1719181,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"